text.autoconfig.elytra_tech.title: Elytra Tech
text.autoconfig.elytra_tech.option.boost:
Elytra Boosting is an alternative to firework rockets, that allows players to use hunger to propel themselves.
It is cheaper and easier than using fireworks, but is substantially less maneuverable.
Elytra Boosting is performed by jumping while elytra flying.
Whether or not Elytra Boosting is enabled
Amount that is added to velocity by boosting
Minimum time between each boost, measured in ticks (1/20ths of a second)
